description: Approval of Reserved Matters for Block A (comprising Block A1 and A2 of 25 storeys and 15 storeys respectively) to provide a total of 193 residential units (comprising 18 studios, 97 one bedroom, 74 two bedroom and 4 three bedroom units) and 518 sq.m (GEA) of retail/restaurant/cafe floorspace (Use Class A1 and A3) and open space (including 'Confluence Place') pursuant to condition 2, relating to siting, design, external appearance and landscaping for the comprehensive mixed use redevelopment of the outline approval DC/06/62375, dated 08 May 2009 for the Lewisham Gateway Site, SE13.
